---
// Who We Are - Impact Focused Layout
---

<section class="py-20 px-4 bg-background">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4">
        Redefining Water Solutions
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-foreground/80 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        A new paradigm for water security, resilience, and prosperity
      </p>
      <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-primary mx-auto mt-6"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Impact Grid -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
      <!-- Mission Statement -->
      <div class="bg-card/50 border border-border/50 rounded-2xl p-8">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-4">Our Why</h3>
        <p class="text-foreground/80 mb-6">
          The Water Foundation exists to address one of the least appreciated challenges of our time: 
          the growing global water crisis and its far-reaching impacts on peace, stability, and prosperity.
        </p>
        <div class="p-4 bg-primary/5 rounded-lg">
          <p class="text-sm text-foreground/80 italic">
            "Where water security is achieved, peace, socio-political stability, and health follow."
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Global Presence -->
      <div class="bg-card/50 border border-border/50 rounded-2xl p-8">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-4">Global Footprint</h3>
        <p class="text-foreground/80 mb-6">
          With teams in Dubai, Delhi, Vaduz, and Munich, we're building a truly global movement 
          to transform water systems and ensure water security for all.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary/10 text-primary rounded-full text-sm">Dubai</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-500/10 text-blue-500 rounded-full text-sm">Delhi</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-teal-500/10 text-teal-500 rounded-full text-sm">Vaduz</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-purple-500/10 text-purple-500 rounded-full text-sm">Munich</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>



    <!-- Call to Action -->
    <div class="text-center">
      <p class="text-foreground/80 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Join us in building a water-resilient future. Together, we can turn the tide on the global water crisis.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-primary text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors">
        Get Involved
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
